::Shadow Wing::

"SHADOW WING MAXIMAIZE!"
She transformed into her bot form. She looked at him for a moment.  Her 
instincts told her that he would be a good allie to have. She smiled a bit 
at having a new friend to talk to.
"Things are different here unlike anything from Cybertron.  But it is 
pleasent here.  You can hunt and play in the forests.  You can swim in the 
lakes and streams.  It's a nice planet to be on. I hope you like it here.  I 
have found this planet to be very beautiful.  I hope ou find it as nice and 
wonderful as I do."
